{"tid":2399980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我之前做手術途中醒左，有冇人試過？","createTime":"2021-02-08T14:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T04:50:35.000Z","uid":218750,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e37d63c56a705fbedaee3b7042087ec7307d590b","tid":2399980,"uid":218750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T14:16:27.000Z","msg":"我入手術室時<br />\n有姑娘同我打麻醉藥同傾偈<br />\n然後畫面一閃就係一個好暗嘅燈光<br />\n眼見手術儀器已經入左身體<br />\n跟住我氣管收縮同身體抽搐<br />\n見到個醫生即時同我對望一眼<br />\n跟手佢聽倒有噴野嘅聲音<br />\n再眼前一黑<br />\n醒返就喺病床上<br />\n覺得成條氣管好痛<br />\n應該係抽搐時整傷<br />\n<br />\n真係有陰影 仲要係私家醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137d05ce15434c80dda49f6099791de07cf3b029","tid":2399980,"uid":235890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T14:17:48.000Z","msg":"姑娘打麻醉藥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77bd4f4ace2502f771cb1de18b648ff741bd88f","tid":2399980,"uid":218750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"137d05ce15434c80dda49f6099791de07cf3b029","tid":2399980,"uid":235890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T14:17:48.000Z","msg":"姑娘打麻醉藥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T14:19:28.000Z","msg":"其實我唔確定係咪麻醉藥<br />\n就係見佢幫我打d入隻手<br />\n跟住就黑畫面"},{"pid":"260d5cd6eb7399ff06a2adcae621fec14d181029","tid":2399980,"uid":362210,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T14:21:03.000Z","msg":"做緊手術醒咗係最大嘅惡夢，等於俾人生劏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89cfcd1a392b4359acfd5366e089b2bb8bfdd24","tid":2399980,"uid":40499,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T14:22:37.000Z","msg":"咁個麻醉師都幾廢"},{"pid":"86e023c4dc250ba6593217c43b58be2192532e28","tid":2399980,"uid":274732,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T14:27:16.000Z","msg":"邊間醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class